1. Core Architecture

Modules / Nodes

Node	Function	Inputs	Outputs	Status

Cave-River Node	Environment baseline & signal calibration	Light, sound, humidity, CO₂	Normalized environment signals	Design ready
AQAROON Home Node	Personal baseline & pattern tracking	Text, MIDI, IMU	Harmonic + sovereignty coordinates	Design ready
MIDI Node	Controller mapping to harmonic / story axes	MIDI hardware	Control signals for UI, harmonics	Prototype planned
INVERSIONZ Protocol	Paradox detection, signal inversion, pattern exploration	Signals, mappers	Reflected / inverted patterns	Design ready
Cosmic Paradox Engine	Meta-pattern orchestration, multi-node synthesis	All signals	Composite metaphysical patterns	Conceptual


Core Concepts

Signal: Atomic input unit

{
    "channel": "text|midi|cave|river",
    "payload": "...",
    "timestamp": "...",
    "context": {...}
}

Baseline: Quiet state per channel; normalizes sensor input

Mapper: Transforms signals → harmonic, sovereignty, story coordinates

Pattern: Symbolic, reusable structures detected across signals



