3. Data Structure

Signal Schema (Canonical)

{
  "channel": "string",
  "payload": "any",
  "timestamp": "ISO8601",
  "context": {
    "node": "string",
    "baseline": "string",
    "mapper": "string",
    "metadata": {}
  }
}

Node Profile

Name

Type (Home/Cave/River/MIDI/etc.)

Baseline reference

Active mappers

Sensor list

Last sync timestamp


Mapper Schema

Mapper ID

Input channels

Output coordinates (harmonic/sovereignty/story)

Calibration params

Last updated



