4. Plugin & Sovereignty Framework

Plugin Rules

Must declare input/output schema

Cannot override baseline without approval

Isolated sandboxed execution

Optional: self-diagnosing / auto-adapting modules


Sovereignty Layer

Ensures privacy and node ownership

Controls multi-node sync (local-first)

Rejects unauthorized agent/plugin changes

Audit logs for all signal transformations



